    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special thanks to Violet. Without her sacrifice, this game would not be here. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything Ends In 0 is a game about the end of the world, but you are not a hero destined to save it. In fact, it can't be saved at all - from the moment you start playing, The World is already doomed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No twist, no fine print, no loopholes, no technicalities. Everything. Will. Die. All you can do is wait for it to be over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And hey! while you're at it, why not strike up a friendly conversation? I hear you're quite similar to a couple of those girls, and quite intriguing to a couple others. Besides, it's not like the awkward moments will really matter in just a little bit. So listen to them for a while, to pass the time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or don't.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Again, it really does not matter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are going to die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CONTROLS (Base game):</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Z] select </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[X] &quot;return&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[ARROWS] lose yourself</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[MOUSE] admire your new forever home</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[W] move forward</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Z] gather<br><br>CONTROLS (Post-Mortem):<br><br>[WASD] move</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[SHIFT] speed up</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[MOUSE] look</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[RMB] toggle cursor+view lock</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[MOUSE WHEEL] zoom</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
